  "texts": [
    "Using the prompts from the held-out dataset, we generate responses from both models and evaluate them to report win scores.",
    "Self-curation significantly enhances DPO performance across all settings compared to no curation as shown in Table 2.",
    "Our method also consistently improves performance for datasets annotated by both humans (Anthropic-HH and Beavertails) and LLMs (UltraFeedback, Orca-DPO and Dolly-DPO).",
    "In particular, the models trained on Anthropic-HH and Beavertails surpass their baselines in both helpfulness and harmlessness evaluations.",
    "See Table 7 and Table 8 for more results."
